42:14.860 --> 42:15.952
I was out.

42:16.000 --> 42:16.898
Just getting back.

42:16.930 --> 42:19.160
Uh, listen, I didn't get
to congratulate you.

42:19.200 --> 42:20.326
The speech went very well.

42:20.370 --> 42:21.735
It did. Thanks.

42:21.770 --> 42:23.863
So, another 48 hours.

42:23.900 --> 42:25.800
Yeah, yeah.
There's a story out

42:25.840 --> 42:27.159
that you're supporting Hamas?

42:27.210 --> 42:29.804
I don't need to worry
about that, do I?

42:29.840 --> 42:32.047
No.
Good.

42:33.680 --> 42:36.114
Um... listen,
I'm not very...

42:36.150 --> 42:40.018
not very good at expressing
my feelings, uh...

42:40.050 --> 42:42.780
so I don't
really like to...

42:44.390 --> 42:46.756
Do you want to come inside?

42:46.790 --> 42:48.655
No, no, no. Ijust...
